

APP FUNCTIONALITY
index.php - Main organizer file
/includes/navigation.controller.php - Navigation functions
/includes/main.controller.php - default controller
/includes/form.controller.php - controller for contact forms
/includes/authorize.php - Authorizes login attempts (SiteOffline)
/includes/widgetDisplay.php - Renders widgets onto app with DisplayWidgetPosition().
/includes/sendmail.php - PHPMailer function to send email



USER CONFIGURATED
config.php - Settings
/styles/style.css - Main CSS style
main.php - Main body frame
/widgets/ - Contains widgets
/pages/ - Contains pages

PRE-DEFINED WIDGETS
	Submenu - See example /widgets/page1_submenu.php
	Contact form - See example /widgets/contactForm.php

AVAILABLE CONTROLLERS
Use config.php to declare controller to pages.
	mainController - default controller. If no controller is declared. This one will be used.
	NavigationController - Only for navigation purpose
	WidgetController - embeded in DisplayWidgetPosition() function
	FormController - Needed if page contains form



